CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Cloudastructure provides an award-winning cloud-based artificial intelligence video surveillance and Remote Guarding service built on AI and machine learning platforms. Our cloud-based solutions allow our customers to provide real-time safety and security solutions for their properties, as well as easily manage security across all of their locations. As of the date of this prospectus, we have contracts in place with five of the top 10 property management companies on the National Multifamily Housing Council's 2024 NMCH 50 list.
